description:
◣◥  Canada Water Parkour Youth Classes!

Let's Jump, Swing, Vault and Climb! Join Our Epic Parkour Class for Kids in East London!" 🏃‍♂️🤸‍♀️🎉

📣 Hey there, East London youth! Are you ready to become a parkour superstar? 🌟 Then come join our new youth parkour class in Canada Water! 

Our expert coaches will teach you all the moves you need to navigate obstacles like a pro, including jumps, vaults, and climbs! 🏃‍♂️🤸‍♀️ Plus, you'll build strength, agility, and confidence, all while having a blast with new friends. 😎 So what are you waiting for? Sign up now and let's get jumping! 🙌 


--- Class Details ---

🗓️ Every Saturday
⏰ 10:30am to 12pm
👦 Ages 8 to 14.
📍 Canada Water, London
